{"tid":343190,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有關NON JUPAS問題想問下","createTime":"2017-08-01T08:50:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T16:26:37.000Z","uid":92951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"552980d4a010cc7a1750d868f4b0c33c1631330f","tid":343190,"uid":92951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T08:50:27.000Z","msg":"我係黎緊會讀hkcc既辣殺<br />\n想問下想第一年non jupas(試下無壞 )既話<br />\nIELTS最好應該幾時考 <br />\n<br />\n同埋個過程上我有D唔明<br />\n上網搵到話9月開始要準備報名<br />\n但我先岩岩開學 試又未考<br />\n跟住又話要IELTS 我知要考<br />\n但應該幾時考同應該準備D文件去報NON JUPAS?<br />\n同埋我呢D year1既係咪報non jupas 既main round?<br />\n咁係咪3月前交資料就OK <br />\n個D咩first round first track對year1 asso仔不適用?<br />\n<br />\n利申<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />SE有FULL CERT<br />\n<br />\n希望有巴絲打解答我既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d14ea9ebf55ae0f19d085c0bc6ee1ae913ce6e","tid":343190,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T09:15:36.000Z","msg":"asso學生等於垃圾？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/293630/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/293630/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n有堆asshole仔喺呢個po度比純正大學生圍剿緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n作為asshole仔嘅你仲唔快啲過去增援?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2f02b9ec2ded7c7bb90d7581b7670843e073cde","tid":343190,"uid":27159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T09:18:22.000Z","msg":"咩科<br />\nb5咩分<br />\n英文幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f73a390a79c64a322300e6f5a0963e3d97112e29","tid":343190,"uid":39845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T09:29:45.000Z","msg":"可以照報first round fast track果啲<br />\n應該間間都可以比你填result pending<br />\n出左gpa再upload上去<br />\nPersonal statement 用心寫<br />\nIelts早啲考好 等你衰左都趕得切再考"},{"pid":"a3ae8bab7a0d787d